Add new user:
    adduser nameofuser
    usermod -aG sudo nameofuser
Install Nginx:
	sudo apt-get update
	sudo apt-get install nginx
Firewall:
	sudo ufw app list      "see the list to use ports"
	sudo ufw allow 'nameofapp'   "allow app"
	sudo ufw status 	     "to see status of firewall"
To check Nginx status:
   systemctl status nginx
To change the index page go to /var/www/html
